{
  "stem": "24409.12",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was informed informally that I should prepare myself to be called up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In about two months, they'd need to-- to active duty.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in the reserve because they could use my capacities.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I would be assigned to-- the idea was to assign me to General Eisenhower's headquarters in Paris.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was actually in-- in Versailles.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't want to go back to Europe yet.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Rafael, my oldest son, had just been born.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Lore was new in America.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I wanted to stay here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, in order to for-- to avoid this, I went to the [INAUDIBLE] office and told him I am very much interested in penology.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I am a psychologist, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I would like to serve in this capacity in the Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, we can use you very much.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We have problems with-- with desertions and just-- just with all kinds of crimes committed by Army people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so they took me and-- and be to it the regular call-up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Before I was-- when I was called up, I was already in the [? north-- ?] in-- in the [? one of ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was ?] go to [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was under the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] is-- inspector general, I think.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Adjutant general, under the adjutant general's office was the penal system.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I became chief psychologist for-- for [INAUDIBLE], where I introduced groups to [INAUDIBLE], unknown then, and persons [? for ?] completely unknown.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it was a [? highly ?] known activity in America.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Lieutenant Colonel.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was retired as a Lieutenant Colonel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in College Park at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't-- not in active duty.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went once every-- once a month, I went to these meetings.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
